1. System Administrator
   a. Total number of users
   b. Total number of stores
   c. Total number of submitted ratings

2. Store Owner

i. Pages to Display
a. Total number of stores added by owner  
 b. View a list of users who have submitted ratings for their store.
c. See the average rating of their store.

ii. Input Details to take from store owner
a. Name
b. Email
c. Address
d. Password

3. Normal User
   i. Pages to Display
   a. Can update their password after logging in.
   b. Can view a list of all registered stores.
   c. Can search for stores by Name and Address.
   d. Store listings should display:
   e. Store Name
   g. gAddress
   h. Overall Rating
   User's Submitted Rating
   Option to submit a rating
   Option to modify their submitted rating
   Can submit ratings (between 1 to 5) for individual stores.
   Can log out from the system.

ii. Input Details to take from User
a. Name
b. Email
c. Address
d. Password
